; Isolate TN LIB.ACT's fixed-address sized byte array declaration.
; Original Action! emits a four-byte descriptor/pointer pair for
; `BYTE ARRAY allocbuf($800)=$2000` before the following current-location PROC.

SET $491=$3000
SET $E=$3000

MODULE

BYTE ARRAY allocbuf($800)=$2000

PROC Main=*()
[$60]
